dataset_id: TES/Aura L3 Atmospheric Temperatures Monthly Gridded V005
title: TES/Aura L3 Atmospheric Temperatures Monthly Gridded V005
summary: Monthly averages of atmospheric temperature and VMR for atmospheric species are provided at 2 deg. lat. X 4 deg. long. spatial grids and at a subset of TES standard pressure levels. Algorithms for deriving TES L3 data will be provided in the data files.
